'[[Me Before You (film)|Me Before You]]''\n| Louisa Clark\n|\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2014/09/gots-emilia-clarke-hunger-games-sam-claflin-to-star-in-mgms-me-before-you-827768/ |title='GOT's Emilia Clarke, 'Hunger Games' Sam Claflin To Star in MGM's 'Me Before You' |last=Fleming |first=Mike |date=2 September 2014 |website=[[Deadline Hollywood]] |publisher=[[Penske Media Corporation]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150725011240/http://deadline.com/2014/09/gots-emilia-clarke-hunger-games-sam-claflin-to-star-in-mgms-me-before-you-827768/ |archive-date=25 July 2015 |access-date=24 July 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2017\n! scope=row| ''[[Voice from the Stone]]''\n| Verena\n|\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{Cite news |last=Siegel |first=Tatiana |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/emilia-clarke-star-indie-psychological-712149 |title=Emilia Clarke to Star in Indie Psychological Thriller 'Voice From the Stone' |date=16 June 2014 |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=19 November 2016 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160219031945/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/emilia-clarke-star-indie-psychological-712149 |archive-date=19 February 2016 |publisher=[[Eldridge Industries#Media holdings|Valence Media]]}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2018\n! scope=row| ''[[Solo: A Star Wars Story]]''\n| [[Qi'ra]]\n|\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.starwars.com/news/emilia-clarke-joins-the-han-solo-stand-alone-film |title=Emilia Clarke Joins the Han Solo Stand-Alone Film |date=18 November 2016 |website=[[Star Wars]] |publisher=[[Lucasfilm]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170129101649/http://www.starwars.com/news/emilia-clarke-joins-the-han-solo-stand-alone-film |archive-date=29 January 2017 |access-date=31 January 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|2018\n! scope=row|''Leading Lady Parts''\n|Herself\n|Short film\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|