10234314/http://www.avclub.com/articles/stench-and-stenchibility%2C102153/ |archive-date=10 November 2013 |access-date=30 September 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2016\n! scope=row|''[[Robot Chicken]]''\n| Bridget (voice)\n| Episode: \"Joel Hurwitz Returns\"\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=\"robotchicken\">{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160812135126/http://www.movienewsguide.com/game-thrones-star-emilia-clarke-shares-secret-overcoming-downsides-fame/224534 |archivedate=12 August 2016 |url=http://www.movienewsguide.com/game-thrones-star-emilia-clarke-shares-secret-overcoming-downsides-fame/224534 |title='Game of Thrones' Star Emilia Clarke Shares Secret on Overcoming The Downsides of Fame |publisher=Movienewsguide.com |date=16 June 2016 |accessdate=20 November 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2017\n! scope=row| ''[[Animals (American TV series)|Animals]]''\n| Lumpy (voice)\n| Episode: \"Rats.\"\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=\"animals\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2017/03/animals-trailer-season-2-hbo-1201788692/ |title='Animals' Trailer: Season 2 Throws Down With Emilia Clarke, Judy Greer, Rupaul and Dan Harmon |last=Nguyen |first=Hanh |date=1 March 2017 |website=[[IndieWire]] |publisher=[[Penske Media Corporation]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301123724/http://www.indiewire.com/2017/03/animals-trailer-season-2-hbo-1201788692/ |archive-date=1 March 2017 |access-date=1 March 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2017\n! scope=row| ''[[Thunderbirds Are Go (TV series)|Thunderbirds Are Go]]''\n| Doyle (voice)\n| Episode: \"Rigged for Disaster\"\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | <ref name=\"thunderbirds\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/news/thunderbirds-are-go-reboot-cast-emilia-clarke-david-tennant-mark-gatiss-game-of-thrones-episodes-a7850741.html |title=Thunderbirds Are Go: Emilia Clarke, David Tennant and Mark Gatiss join ITV reboot |last=Martin |first=Matilda |date=20 July 2017 |